    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Family of small- to medium-sized birds, including coots, crakes, and gallinules. Many species are associated with wetlands, although members are also found in many terrestrial habitats.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
